subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution
. Known from low latitudinal areas in the Indo-West Pacific and Atlantic Oceans; mesopelagic to near bottom, at depths of 
291–3292 m
, but commonly found between 300 and 
600 m
(
Crosnier & Forest, 1973
; 
Chace 1986
; 
Chan & Yu, 1986
; 
Crosnier, 1987
; 
Cardoso & Young, 2005
).
